==Starting off==
===Talking to Fred the Farmer===
* {{tselect|Ask about Halloween Event?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' Hello, Fred. Is everything alright?
** '''Fred the Farmer:''' Oh, hello there! Actually, no, everything's not alright. I've made a terrible mistake...
** '''Player:''' What kind of mistake?
** '''Fred the Farmer:''' The Spook-a-thon Decoration Contest! Hosted by Death himself! I signed up weeks ago, thinking I had all the time in the world...
** '''Fred the Farmer:''' But now I've realised, I've got no idea how to make my house spooky enough to compete! I could really use some help pulling this together!
** {{tselect|Start the Halloween event?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' I suppose I could lend a hand. Any ideas where to start?
*** '''Fred the Farmer:''' Well... there's Seth Groats, just across the river to the east. His place is decorated with a lot of spooky charm. Maybe we could get some inspiration from his decorations.
*** '''Player:''' Sounds easy enough, I'll go and see him.
*** '''Fred the Farmer:''' Thank you! You might just save my haunted house dreams, and help me win the contest.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I'd love to help, but I'm a bit busy at the moment. I'll return when I can.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.|event=no}}

===Talking to Fred after starting the event===
