===Talking to Seth Groats===
* {{tselect|Ask about Halloween Event?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' Morning! Your place looks incredible! The cobwebs, the pumpkin... and is that a moving chair?
** '''Seth Groats:''' Ha! Took some effort, that's for sure. Not many folks are brave enough to venture out and obtain those spooky decorations. This type of adventure isn't for the faint hearted!
** '''Player:''' It's honestly impressive. I've never seen decorations like these before. Where do you even find this stuff?
** '''Seth Groats:''' Hmph... trying to pry my secrets out, are you? Most folk wouldn't have the nerve to track 'em down.
** '''Player:''' I'm just curious! This place is inspiring.
** '''Seth Groats:''' Well, I suppose I can give you a few hints. First up, Death himself has plenty of creepy decorations. Next, the moving chair can be found in Draynor Manor, if you've got the spine to search it.
** '''Seth Groats:''' Finally, Sarah at the farm near Falador has been making some Halloween decorations. If you're lucky, you might be able to get her to part with something.
** '''Seth Groats:''' Oh, and I guess you can take this spooky picture. I had it up last year, but it gave my cows nightmares.
** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
*** '''Seth Groats:''' Oh, looks like you've got no space for it. I'll hold onto it until you do.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tact|receives= a [[Spooky picture (2025 Halloween event)|Spooky picture]]}}
<!--a spooky picture must be acquired before the player can get the other decorations-->
** '''Player:''' Cows can have nightmares? That's news to me. Thanks for the information, Seth. I'll go have a look for those items now.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.|event=no}}

===Talking to Seth again after receiving the picture for the first time===
* {{tselect|Ask about Halloween Event?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** {{tcond|If the player lost the spooky picture:}}
*** '''Player:''' I lost the spooky picture.
*** '''Seth Groats:''' Lost it already? Lucky for you, I've got a spare tucked away. You can have this one.
*** {{tact|continues}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has all the other decorations:}}
**** {{tbox|You have acquired a spooky picture, a chair, scarecrow and wall lamp. You should return to Fred in Lumbridge.}}
<!--Only happens when a player loses the spooky picture, gets all the other items, but then needs to grab the picture once again-->
**** {{tact|receives= a [[Spooky picture (2025 Halloween event)|Spooky picture]]}}
**** {{tact|continues}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has no inventory space:}}
**** '''Seth Groats:''' Oh, looks like you've got no space for it. I'll hold onto it until you do.
**** {{tact|continues}}
** {{tcond|If the player has not acquired the other decorations yet:}}
