*** '''Seth Groats:''' Finally, Sarah at the farm near Falador has been crafting some Halloween decorations.
*** '''Player:''' Thanks!
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player acquired all of the other decorations:}}
*** {{tact|below}}
